  "description": "Improve News Card Component Visual Design\n\nEnhance the news card component to improve its visual hierarchy, typography, and spacing for better readability and aesthetic appeal.\n\nRequirements:\n- Increase visual hierarchy to make key elements (headline, image, metadata) more prominent and scannable\n- Fix typography issues: ensure appropriate font sizes, weights, and line heights for headlines, body text, and metadata\n- Adjust padding and spacing: improve internal padding within the card and spacing between elements (image, title, description, metadata)\n- Ensure consistent margins between cards in grid/list layouts\n- Verify responsive behavior across mobile, tablet, and desktop breakpoints\n- Maintain visual consistency with existing design system if applicable\n- Test with various content lengths (short and long headlines, with/without images)",
